  "text": "LOD and LOQ tests for the procedure were performed on samples containing progressively more dilute concentrations of analyte. Afterwards, the concentrations versus the RSD obtained for area from each of the concentrations were plotted in order to determine LOD and LOQ [CITATION_1] .",
